    "Deep learning techniques have been widely applied across various subareas of software engineering and have achieved impressive results.",
    "First, deep learning techniques typically improve the performance of most tasks.",
    "For example, deep learning-based code clone detection always achieves higher recall and better precision than the best classical approaches.",
